cs.LG, cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.SY, cs.AI 

The paper proposes a framework that combines deep reinforcement learning and power control in wireless networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) and cs.IT (Information Theory). The paper also involves policy gradient descent algorithm and reward function, which are related to control and optimization, making cs.SY (Systems and Control) a possible category. Finally, the use of deep neural networks suggests cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as another possible category.
